    "The top D 1 numbers are selected from the sentence representation to store in a new list by the original index orders, which is set as pruned sentence embedding.",
    "Therefore, the dimensionality of the pruned sentence representation is D 1.",
    "Pruning on Correlated Words Level of AQE (WQE)WQE primarily achieves sentence dimensionality reduction by directly pruning the semantically smaller values from the embedding of the correlated words.",
    "We select the top D 2 numbers from the correlated word embedding |w i w i+1 to store in a new list by the original index orders.",
    "The new list is defined as the embedding of the pruned correlated words."
